{"tid":2027513,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【爆煲危機】中國企業違約危機急擴散 《彭博》：高負債見真考驗","createTime":"2020-05-21T11:59:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T00:40:40.000Z","uid":141151,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e644b61b431e1f649a57eba2e99ffe22579705c4","tid":2027513,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T11:59:46.000Z","msg":"【爆煲危機】中國企業違約危機急擴散 《彭博》：高負債見真考驗<br />\n<br />\n2016年中國為打壓金融市場風險而展開去槓桿計劃，影子銀行及資產管理行業作為企業撲水渠道均被打壓，融資更見困難，惟債務危機仍未過去。經歷武漢肺炎疫情後，中國再加大負債以支撐經濟，中國企業目前正面臨考驗，債券違約數量創下紀錄新高。《彭博》報道提及中國企業近10年累積龐大債務的原因與當中危機，以及中國處理這些問題方面的困難。<br />\n<br />\n全文請參閱蘋果<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200521/SE26KM5WIQOHC7FOPRA5KGRLT4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200521%2FSE26KM5WIQOHC7FOPRA5KGRLT4%2F&d=%2FbZU6AtRr1oB2SY8YhhoV27D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=ba6222bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200521%2FSE26KM5WIQOHC7FOPRA5KGRLT4%2F&h=506783fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200521/SE26KM5WIQOHC7FOPRA5KGRLT4/</a>"},{"pid":"f320779f042d69db5c90918aa87e020ad7d4f297","tid":2027513,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T12:01:12.000Z","msg":"海洋公園先比50億 過到骨再拎mpf 拎外匯儲備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10c45668b7d83be092f64523a5b70a35e1166043","tid":2027513,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T12:02:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8gLBp9Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8gLBp9Z.jpg&h=b5c1741c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6480946458662f63c5e2ade534a189b204596212","tid":2027513,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T12:03:31.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n［Twitter］港版國安法殺到，外資勢必撤資！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fvBGBS\"